The paper proposes a novel hyperspectral unmixing scheme based on a two-staged autoencoder network with additional layers and a projection metric. This involves machine learning techniques such as deep learning and optimization methods. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
